  "title": "Amethyst - Stardew Valley Wiki",
  "description": "Amethyst is a Mineral that can be obtained from Amethyst Nodes and Gem Nodes in the Mines, from the purple Gem Bird on Ginger Island during rainy days, from panning, or as a rare drop from Green Slimes. It has a 10% chance to be dropped by a slain Dwarvish Sentry in the Volcano Dungeon. It may also occasionally be found in Fishing Treasure Chests or in a Garbage Can. A Super Cucumber Fish Pond may produce 1-3 Amethyst when the population of the pond reaches 9. The Statue Of Endless Fortune produces one Amethyst per year, on Abigail's birthday, Fall 13.",
